# device.te — SELinux type declarations for AETHER device-specific objects.
#
# Each `type X dev_type, …` line registers a new SELinux type that
# file_contexts can refer to. The base types (hal_sensors_default,
# hal_camera_default, etc.) are inherited from AOSP's system/sepolicy/.

# AETHER paravirt device nodes (ch12 modem + sensor shared pages, ch47 HVC
# vendor calls). Surfaced under /dev/aether/.
type aether_device, dev_type;
